name: Tilly The Killer Whale
description: $TILLY is based on Tilikum, who was a captive male orca who spent most of his life at SeaWorld Orlando in Florida. We are an experimented team of devs and ops managers that aim at bringing the $TILLY meme token to life and building a unique community centered around it. We want to build a fun, elevated and respectful community through our deliverables in terms of content, participation and contests involving our members.
